You know that I'm on top of you.</i>

709
01:10:43,128 --> 01:10:46,048
Do not attempt to grow a brain.

710
01:10:55,349 --> 01:10:59,061
- So I guess there's a plan now?
- Could be.

711
01:10:59,144 --> 01:11:01,313
- Yeah?
