759
01:15:29,790 --> 01:15:33,585
- We can get to his place inside of 15 minutes.
- Jack, get out of there.

760
01:15:33,669 --> 01:15:36,296
- We're going after the source.
- Watch your back.

761
01:15:38,298 --> 01:15:39,383
Wait for me!

762
01:15:40,050 --> 01:15:42,552
Mac, get me outta here.

763
01:15:54,898 --> 01:15:58,777
Somebody go to the back and check
and see if he came out the back. Go!

764
01:16:10,247 --> 01:16:12,666
<i>- Can you see him?
- He's not behind us.</i>

765
01:16:12,749 --> 01:16:14,876
- What?
- He's not back here.

766
01:16:14,960 --> 01:16:16,378
Oh, my God. Go look!

767
01:16:16,461 --> 01:16:20,841
Lay down and look under the bus
and see if you can see him down there.

768
01:16:22,050 --> 01:16:23,635
