<i>He's all right! He's all right!</i>

782
01:17:45,092 --> 01:17:48,470
Hold my legs. Hold my legs.
Somebody hold my legs.

783
01:17:48,553 --> 01:17:50,639
Hold his legs.

784
01:17:51,056 --> 01:17:53,225
<i>- Hold his legs!
- Come on!</i>

785
01:17:55,102 --> 01:17:57,312
Come on! I got ya!

786
01:18:01,733 --> 01:18:06,363
<i>- Is he hurt? Is he OK?
- Pull! Pull!</i>

787
01:18:06,446 --> 01:18:08,532
Come on! Come on!

788
01:18:08,615 --> 01:18:10,993
We got him now. Come on, pull!

789
01:18:12,118 --> 01:18:14,078
Jesus. I can't believe it.

790
01:18:16,580 --> 01:18:19,333
You are a complete jerk. You know that?

791
01:18:21,168 --> 01:18:24,839
- Did you have any luck with the bomb?
- Yeah. It didn't go off.

792
01:18:26,424 --> 01:18:27,591
<i>Ortiz, thanks.</i>

793
01:18:27,675 --> 01:18:30,761
How many lives you got, man?

794
01:18:31,387 --> 01:18:36,852
<i>You're not too bright, man,
but you got some big, round, hairy cojones.</i>

795
01:18:38,520 --> 01:18:42,024
That's... very gross, Ortiz.

796
01:18:43,400 --> 01:18:45,902
Can't even pay him a compliment.

797
01:18:46,987 --> 01:18:50,198
- How you doing?
- You scared the shit out of me, Jack!

798
01:18:50,282 --> 01:18:52,534
Other than that, I'm fine.

799
01:18:52,618 --> 01:18:56,204
- What is that smell?
- It's gas.

800
01:18:56,288 --> 01:18:58,790
- We're leaking gas?
