915
01:32:19,341 --> 01:32:21,385
Here comes the cavalry.

916
01:32:37,484 --> 01:32:39,987
- How ya doing?
- We're OK.

917
01:32:42,114 --> 01:32:45,659
I just might be a nice guy
and let you have the rest of the day off.

918
01:32:45,742 --> 01:32:47,786
Oh, boy.

919
01:32:47,869 --> 01:32:50,622
Mac, this is Annie.

920
01:32:50,706 --> 01:32:53,875
Annie, meet Lieutenant McMahon.

921
01:32:53,959 --> 01:32:56,044
- How you doing?
- OK.

922
01:32:56,378 --> 01:32:59,548
- This should take care of it.
- Ow!

923
01:32:59,631 --> 01:33:02,718
- Watch it.
- Sorry.

924
01:33:02,801 --> 01:33:06,179
- We're gonna have you guys checked out.
- Lieutenant!

925
01:33:07,806 --> 01:33:10,642
It's him. He wants to know
when he's gonna get his money.

926
01:33:10,726 --> 01:33:13,688
I'll tell him what to do
with his goddamn money.

927
01:33:13,771 --> 01:33:16,274
He doesn't know it blew up.

928
01:33:19,611 --> 01:33:20,987
30 minutes.

929
01:34:01,151 --> 01:34:03,236
I'll be right back.

930
01:34:06,156 --> 01:34:12,037
All right, here's our target. Fox, I want you
in 4-1, you in 1-2. You're in 3. Let's move it.

931
01:34:12,120 --> 01:34:15,415
